Kusalattika, Upādānadukādi
40.
88Nakusalaṃ noupādānaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā ekūnatiṃsa, ārammaṇe catuvīsa…pe…  vipāke nava…pe…  avigate ekūnatiṃsa.
89Nakusalaṃ nanoupādānaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ. Sabbattha nava. Vipākaṃ natthi.)
